WEBVTT

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:02.280
Queer and trans people, immoral.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:05.296
Indigenous people, savage.

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:07.376
Women and girls as property.

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:10.896
And when they fail to see our bodies
as some mother's child,

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:14.496
it becomes easier to ban us,

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:15.736
detain us,

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:16.976
deport us,

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:18.776
imprison us,

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:22.480
sacrifice us for the illusion of security.

00:10:26.640 --> 00:10:31.360
(Applause)